<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٥٨٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3784">عَبْدَانُ </a>أَخْبَرَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4266">أَبِي، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4042">عَبْدِ الْمَلِكِ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1182">جُنْدَبًا </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«أَنَا فَرَطُكُمْ عَلَى الْحَوْضِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>